import {STEPS} from "./Steps";

const {
    SELECT_REASON,
    PURCHASE_DETAILS,
    TRANSACTION_DETAILS,
    ATTACHMENT,
    DESCRIPTION,
    THANK_YOU,
    PURCHASE_INCORRECT,
    PURCHASE_RETURNED_OR_COMPANY,
    ERROR_PURCHASE_RETURNED_OR_COMPANY,
    SELECT_TRANSACTION,
    SHOW_INFO_ABOUT_TRANSACTION
} = STEPS
const FLOWS_LIST = {

    noTransaction: {
        normal: [
            SELECT_REASON,
            PURCHASE_DETAILS,
            TRANSACTION_DETAILS,
            ATTACHMENT,
            THANK_YOU
        ],
        noTransactionPurchaseIncorrect: [
            PURCHASE_INCORRECT
        ]
    },
    differentAmount: {
        normal: [
            SELECT_REASON,
            TRANSACTION_DETAILS,
            ATTACHMENT,
            DESCRIPTION,
            THANK_YOU
        ]
    },
    status: {
        normal: [
            SELECT_REASON,
            TRANSACTION_DETAILS,
            ATTACHMENT,
            DESCRIPTION,
            THANK_YOU
        ]
    },
    cashbackRejected: {
        normal: [
            SELECT_REASON,
            PURCHASE_RETURNED_OR_COMPANY,
            TRANSACTION_DETAILS,
            ATTACHMENT,
            THANK_YOU
        ],
        error: [
            ERROR_PURCHASE_RETURNED_OR_COMPANY
        ]
    },
    payout: {
        normal: [
            SELECT_REASON,
            SELECT_TRANSACTION,
            SHOW_INFO_ABOUT_TRANSACTION,
            THANK_YOU
        ],
        askAboutTransaction: [
            SELECT_REASON,
            SELECT_TRANSACTION,
            SHOW_INFO_ABOUT_TRANSACTION,
            DESCRIPTION,
            THANK_YOU
        ],
        noTransactions: [
            SELECT_REASON,
            SELECT_TRANSACTION,
            DESCRIPTION,
            THANK_YOU
        ],
        differentStatus: [
            SELECT_REASON,
            SELECT_TRANSACTION,
            DESCRIPTION,
            THANK_YOU
        ]
    },
    other: {
        normal: [
            SELECT_REASON,
            DESCRIPTION,
            ATTACHMENT,
            THANK_YOU
        ]
    }
}

export default FLOWS_LIST
